events.title: Graduation
events.content: After graduating from Imperial High School, I started my journey to adulthood. Got my first job and started my education at Imperial Valley College

events.title: College Graduate
events.content: I finished my associates in administration of justice. I realized it wasn't fulfilling. I decided to enroll in a web development bootcamp at UCSD extension. I learned how to code javascript, html, css, use react, bootstrap, some database like sql, mongodb. Assignments taught me to work with a team on deadlines to create full stack applications.

events.title: The Present
events.content: Currently trying to find myself in the tech world. I started to self teach myself python and currently reenrolled in college to get my associates in cyber security. I hope to potentially get a role in this field and I will continue to update this site with certifications and updated work.
